    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="stream__buffer_8h" kindref="compound">stream_buffer.h</ref></para>
<para><preformatted>
size_t <ref refid="stream__buffer_8h_1af32d1737de29f24ee31ac1e3c407d9fd" kindref="member">xStreamBufferBytesAvailable( StreamBufferHandle_t xStreamBuffer )</ref>;
</preformatted></para>
<para>Queries a stream buffer to see how much data it contains, which is equal to the number of bytes that can be read from the stream buffer before the stream buffer would be empty.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>xStreamBuffer</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The handle of the stream buffer being queried.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>The number of bytes that can be read from the stream buffer before the stream buffer would be empty. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
